{
  "book": 20,
  "chapter": 6,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "heading": "更多的警告"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "My son, if you have become surety for your neighbor, Have given a pledge for a stranger, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "My son, if you have become surety for your neighbor, Have given a pledge for a stranger,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "If you have been snared with the words of your mouth, Have been caught with the words of your mouth, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "If you have been snared with the words of your mouth, Have been caught with the words of your mouth,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Do this then, my son, and deliver yourself; Since you have come into the hand of your neighbor, Go, humble yourself, and importune your neighbor. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Do this then, my son, and deliver yourself; Since you have come into the hand of your neighbor, Go, humble yourself, and importune your neighbor."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Do this then, my son, and deliver yourself; Since you have come into the hand of your neighbor, Go, humble yourself, and importune your neighbor."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Give no sleep to your eyes, Nor slumber to your eyelids; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Give no sleep to your eyes, Nor slumber to your eyelids;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Deliver yourself like a gazelle from the hunter’s hand And like a bird from the hand of the fowler. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Deliver yourself like a gazelle from the hunter’s hand And like a bird from the hand of the fowler."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Go to the ant, O sluggard, Observe her ways and be wise, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Go to the ant, O sluggard, Observe her ways and be wise,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Which, having no chief, Officer or ruler, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Which, having no chief, Officer or ruler,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Prepares her food in the summer And gathers her provision in the harvest. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Prepares her food in the summer And gathers her provision in the harvest."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "How long will you lie down, O sluggard? When will you arise from your sleep? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "How long will you lie down, O sluggard? When will you arise from your sleep?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“A little sleep, a little slumber, A little folding of the hands to rest”— "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“A little sleep, a little slumber, A little folding of the hands to rest”—"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Your poverty will come in like a vagabond And your need like an armed man. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Your poverty will come in like a vagabond And your need like an armed man."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "A worthless person, a wicked man, Is the one who walks with a perverse mouth, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "A worthless person, a wicked man, Is the one who walks with a perverse mouth,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Who winks with his eyes, who signals with his feet, Who points with his fingers; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Who winks with his eyes, who signals with his feet, Who points with his fingers;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Who winks with his eyes, who signals with his feet, Who points with his fingers;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Who with perversity in his heart continually devises evil, Who spreads strife. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Who with perversity in his heart continually devises evil, Who spreads strife."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Who with perversity in his heart continually devises evil, Who spreads strife."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Therefore his calamity will come suddenly; Instantly he will be broken and there will be no healing. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Therefore his calamity will come suddenly; Instantly he will be broken and there will be no healing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "There are six things which the Lord hates, Yes, seven which are an abomination to Him: "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "There are six things which the Lord hates, Yes, seven which are an abomination to Him:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Haughty eyes, a lying tongue, And hands that shed innocent blood, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Haughty eyes, a lying tongue, And hands that shed innocent blood,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Haughty eyes, a lying tongue, And hands that shed innocent blood,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "A heart that devises wicked plans, Feet that run rapidly to evil, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "A heart that devises wicked plans, Feet that run rapidly to evil,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "A false witness who utters lies, And one who spreads strife among brothers. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "A false witness who utters lies, And one who spreads strife among brothers."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "heading": "警告勿犯淫亂"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "My son, observe the commandment of your father And do not forsake the teaching of your mother; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "My son, observe the commandment of your father And do not forsake the teaching of your mother; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Bind them continually on your heart; Tie them around your neck. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Bind them continually on your heart; Tie them around your neck."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When you walk about, they will guide you; When you sleep, they will watch over you; And when you awake, they will talk to you. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When you walk about, they will guide you; When you sleep, they will watch over you; And when you awake, they will talk to you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When you walk about, they will guide you; When you sleep, they will watch over you; And when you awake, they will talk to you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For the commandment is a lamp and the teaching is light; And reproofs for discipline are the way of life "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For the commandment is a lamp and the teaching is light; And reproofs for discipline are the way of life"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "To keep you from the evil woman, From the smooth tongue of the adulteress. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "To keep you from the evil woman, From the smooth tongue of the adulteress."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Do not desire her beauty in your heart, Nor let her capture you with her eyelids. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Do not desire her beauty in your heart, Nor let her capture you with her eyelids."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For on account of a harlot one is reduced to a loaf of bread, And an adulteress hunts for the precious life. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For on account of a harlot one is reduced to a loaf of bread, And an adulteress hunts for the precious life."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Can a man take fire in his bosom And his clothes not be burned? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Can a man take fire in his bosom And his clothes not be burned?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Or can a man walk on hot coals And his feet not be scorched? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Or can a man walk on hot coals And his feet not be scorched?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "So is the one who goes in to his neighbor’s wife; Whoever touches her will not go unpunished. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "So is the one who goes in to his neighbor’s wife; Whoever touches her will not go unpunished."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Men do not despise a thief if he steals To satisfy himself when he is hungry; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Men do not despise a thief if he steals To satisfy himself when he is hungry;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But when he is found, he must repay sevenfold; He must give all the substance of his house. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But when he is found, he must repay sevenfold; He must give all the substance of his house."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The one who commits adultery with a woman is lacking sense; He who would destroy himself does it. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The one who commits adultery with a woman is lacking sense; He who would destroy himself does it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Wounds and disgrace he will find, And his reproach will not be blotted out. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Wounds and disgrace he will find, And his reproach will not be blotted out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For jealousy enrages a man, And he will not spare in the day of vengeance. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For jealousy enrages a man, And he will not spare in the day of vengeance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He will not accept any ransom, Nor will he be satisfied though you give many gifts. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He will not accept any ransom, Nor will he be satisfied though you give many gifts."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
